      <akn:section eId="sec_28:2_206">
        <akn:num>28:2-206</akn:num>
        <akn:heading>Offer and acceptance in formation of contract.</akn:heading>
<akn:subsection eId="subsec_28:2-206_1">
      <akn:num>(1)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>Unless otherwise unambiguously indicated by the language or circumstances:</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_28:2-206_2">
      <akn:num>(2)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>Where the beginning of a requested performance is a reasonable mode of acceptance an offeror who is not notified of acceptance within a reasonable time may treat the offer as having lapsed before acceptance.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection>
      </akn:section>
